<arggraph id="micro_c102" topic_id="books_obsolete" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Paper and books, at some point will become obsolete.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[It is far more convenient and takes up a lot less space to store data on hard drives and disks than to use paper products.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[Paper can deteriorate if improperly stored,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[making it inconvenient in many situations.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[Paper products also cannot be accessed remotely,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[giving it a huge disadvantage compared to storing information digitally.]]></edu>
